com.energyxxer.commodore.module

Class Namespace

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.energyxxer.commodore.module.Namespace

  • public class Namespace
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a namespace inside a command module, containing all the elements that belong to it, including, but not limited to, types, tags and functions.
    See Also:
    CommandModule, FunctionManager, TagManager, TypeManager
